{"article_id":"1nyuqrXwQRWfAHDM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama said Sunday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that Hillary Clinton showed \" carelessness \"","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"by using a private email server ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"but he also strongly defended his former secretary of state ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"she did not endanger national security ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"while also vowing","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that an ongoing FBI investigation into the matter will not be tainted by politics .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"In an interview on \" Fox News Sunday , \" Mr. Obama seemed to prejudge the outcome of the ongoing inquiry into Mrs. Clinton ' s email scandal ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and he disputed the notion","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that any of the emails contained classified information of true importance .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" She would never intentionally put America in any kind of jeopardy , \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" What I also know is that there ' s classified","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and then there ' s classified .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"There ' s stuff","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that is really top secret top secret ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and then there ' s stuff","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that is being presented to the president , the secretary of state ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"you may not want going out over the wire . \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"But Mr. Obama also conceded","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that Mrs. Clinton used poor judgment","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"in choosing to conduct official business through a private account","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"rather than use a State.gov address .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Mrs. Clinton herself has said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that was a poor choice","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and she wishes","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"she had done things differently .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" I continue to believe","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"she has not jeopardized America ' s national security , \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"the president said .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"\" There ' s a carelessness","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"in terms of managing emails","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that she has owned","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and she recognizes .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"But I also think","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"it is important to keep this in perspective . \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"More than 2,000 emails","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that passed through Mrs. Clinton ' s account","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"now are marked classified ,","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"and nearly two dozen contained top secret information .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"The FBI is investigating the matter ,","depth":3},{"id":42,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"while Mrs. Clinton has virtually promised","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"she will not be indicted ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"the scandal still hangs over her presidential ambitions","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"and fuels the notion","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"- widespread ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"according to opinion polls -","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that she ' s not trustworthy .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"She maintains","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that no emails in the account were classified at the time","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"they were sent or received -","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"though she was initially much more emphatic ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"flatly saying","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"she had never handled classified information .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"She reiterated last week","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that , in her view , the federal investigation ultimately will clear her .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"\" That is not going to happen , \"","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"she told NBC News","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"when asked","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"if she would be indicted .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"\" There is not even the remotest chance","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"that it ' s going to happen . \"","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Critics were quick to jump on Mr. Obama ' s defense of Mrs. Clinton ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the president is grasping at straws","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"by focusing on differences in how emails are classified .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"\" The president twisted himself into a pretzel","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"spinning his former secretary of state ' s mishandling of classified material , \"","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"said Michael Short , a spokesman for the Republican National Committee .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Republicans also have charged","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"that Mr. Obama ' s Justice Department will be hesitant to bring charges against Mrs. Clinton","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"because doing so would torpedo her presidential aspirations .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Mrs. Clinton is locked in a tough race with Sen. Bernard Sanders of Vermont for the Democratic Party ' s presidential nomination , with the possibility of a general election","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"to follow .","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"The president dismissed that criticism","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"and promised in no uncertain terms","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"that the FBI probe will be free from all political interference .","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"\" I guarantee","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"there is no political influence in any investigation","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"conducted by the Justice Department of the FBI ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"not just in this case","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"but in any case , \"","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"\" Full stop , period , guaranteed .","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"Nobody gets treated differently","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"when it comes to the Justice Department","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"because nobody is above the law . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":177,"left":152,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":129,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":125,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":96,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":91,"right":95,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":0,"right":90,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":90,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":3,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":107,"right":123,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":98,"right":106,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":8,"right":97,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":99,"right":105,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":100,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":101,"right":103,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":17,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":110,"right"